<template>
  <select>
    <option v-for="item in data" :key="item[this.propKey]" value="{{item[this.propValue]}}">{{item[this.propValue]}}</option>
  </select>
</template>
<script>
import axios from 'axios'
export default {
  props: {
    url: String,
    propKey: String,
    propValue: String,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      data: [],
    }
  },
  created(){
    axios.get(this.url)
    .then(res => {
      this.data = res.data;
      console.log(res);
    })
    .catch(err => {
      console.error(err); 
    })
  }
}
</script>
<style scoped>
</style>
